  "title": "Question on the page \"rangeSlider\"",
  "body": "Hi! I have a documentation issue on InstantSearch.js. I could not find what I was looking for on the page \"[rangeSlider](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/widgets/rangeSlider.html)\".\r\n\r\nI have an issue with the rangeSlider widget where it only works on the price field.\r\nI have included the taxonomy for my field ABV to my indices and I can see the choices as checkbox option on the site but when I try to use the rangeSlider widget similar to price field, it won’t return any hits from the API",
